NTSC USERS

If you are an NTSC Amiga user, I'm sorry, but currently you can't open
Maped in 640x200 (NTSC or DPLNTSC).
MapEd require a 640x256 display (PAL or DPLPAL).

I'll try to add a ScreenMode-Requester in the next version.



