 KNOWN BUGS

- This is not really a bug... This is an Amiga DOS "notify" feature:
  due to some technical reasons, when MapEd detect that the Blocks File
  has changed, it try to re-load it.  If it is corrupted, wrong, or it
  doesn't exists anymore, no error messages can be displayed...  I'll try
  to fix this in next MapEd versions...


I think there are so many other bugs that this page would not be enough...
:-)

Remember:
- No many checks are performed!
- PLEASE Don't run MapEd on 1.3 (or lower) systems!




